cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.CV. 

The paper deals with training very deep neural networks, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. The use of a layer-parallel multigrid solver and the interpretation of the training problem as a problem of optimal control suggest that the paper may belong to the cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) or cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-categories. However, the focus on neural networks and the investigation of initialization strategies make cs.LG (Machine Learning) the most likely sub-category. The use of deep networks and the study of their sensitivity to hyperparameters and randomness in initial network parameters also suggest that the paper may belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-categories.
